                        %p.eyebrow User Flows
                        %h3 How users shop for dog food
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p To design an experience that actually works for dog owners, I needed to understand how they shop, what they know walking in, what they're unsure about, and where they might get stuck. Mapping these flows helped ensure every path feels intuitive and leads to the right food for their dog.
