                    %h4 Education & Trust Building
                    %p Pet parents exploring holistic nutrition usually have a lot of questions before they're ready to buy. These pages are designed to meet them there, bringing together education, brand values, and real customer stories in a way that feels honest and reassuring. By the time someone finishes exploring, the goal is that they feel informed enough to take the next step with confidence.
